<br>
Very pretty game, just very unfinished, semi buggy, and not worth 50 bucks in it's current state.  Heck of alot of fun from the awed newbie PoV, but I could see myself getting bored enough too soon.  LOTS of fun stuff to do really, but like AO you'll be doing the same stuff at level 1 when you're level 100, it seems, and all solo if you want.<br>
